meta.title: Lingo.dev - Ihinduranya ry'indimi rikoresheje ubwenge bwite bwa mudasobwa ku buhanga bwo ku rubuga na telefoni
meta.description: Ihinduranya ry'indimi ry'ikoranabuhanga rigezweho ku buhanga, mu buryo bwa CI/CD. Ohereza vuba, sohoramo kenshi, kandi ugire abakiriya benshi bashyura.
